{"data":[{"name":"80:1","price":"അദ്ദേഹം മുഖം ചുളിച്ചു തിരിഞ്ഞുകളഞ്ഞു.","arabic":"عَبَسَ وَتَوَلَّىٰٓ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5759,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿabasa watawallā ","translations":["He frowned","and turned away","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿabasa","watawallā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,790],[2,790,2185]]}},{"name":"80:2","price":"അദ്ദേഹത്തിന്‍റെ (നബിയുടെ) അടുത്ത് ആ അന്ധന്‍ വന്നതിനാല്‍.","arabic":"أَن جَآءَهُ ٱلۡأَعۡمَىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5760,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"an jāahu al-aʿmā ","translations":["Because","came to him","the blind man","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["an","jāahu","al-aʿmā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,630],[2,630,3530],[3,3530,4575]]}},{"name":"80:3","price":"(നബിയേ,) നിനക്ക് എന്തറിയാം? അയാള്‍ (അന്ധന്‍) ഒരു വേള പരിശുദ്ധി പ്രാപിച്ചേക്കാമല്ലോ?","arabic":"وَمَا يُدۡرِيكَ لَعَلَّهُۥ يَزَّكَّىٰٓ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5761,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā yud'rīka laʿallahu yazzakkā ","translations":["But what","would make you know","that he might","purify himself","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","yud'rīka","laʿallahu","yazzakkā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,700],[2,700,1770],[3,1770,2980],[4,2980,4465]]}},{"name":"80:4","price":"അല്ലെങ്കില്‍ ഉപദേശം സ്വീകരിക്കുകയും, ആ ഉപദേശം അയാള്‍ക്ക് പ്രയോജനപ്പെടുകയും ചെയ്തേക്കാമല്ലോ.","arabic":"أَوۡ يَذَّكَّرُ فَتَنفَعَهُ ٱلذِّكۡرَىٰٓ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5762,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"aw yadhakkaru fatanfaʿahu al-dhik'rā ","translations":["Or","be reminded","so would benefit him","the reminder","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["aw","yadhakkaru","fatanfaʿahu","al-dhik'rā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,420],[2,420,1670],[3,1670,3590],[4,3590,5265]]}},{"name":"80:5","price":"എന്നാല്‍ സ്വയം പര്യാപ്തത നടിച്ചവനാകട്ടെ","arabic":"أَمَّا مَنِ ٱسۡتَغۡنَىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5763,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"ammā mani is'taghnā ","translations":["As for","(him) who","considers himself free from need","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["ammā","mani","is'taghnā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1460],[2,1460,1850],[3,1850,2995]]}},{"name":"80:6","price":"നീ അവന്‍റെ നേരെ ശ്രദ്ധതിരിക്കുന്നു.","arabic":"فَأَنتَ لَهُۥ تَصَدَّىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5764,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-anta lahu taṣaddā ","translations":["So you","to him","give attention","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-anta","lahu","taṣaddā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1500],[2,1500,2070],[3,2070,3385]]}},{"name":"80:7","price":"അവന്‍ പരിശുദ്ധി പ്രാപിക്കാതിരിക്കുന്നതിനാല്‍ നിനക്കെന്താണ് കുറ്റം?","arabic":"وَمَا عَلَيۡكَ أَلَّا يَزَّكَّىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5765,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā ʿalayka allā yazzakkā ","translations":["And not","upon you","that not","he purifies himself","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","ʿalayka","allā","yazzakkā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,650],[2,650,1550],[3,1550,2450],[4,2450,3885]]}},{"name":"80:8","price":"എന്നാല്‍ നിന്‍റെ അടുക്കല്‍ ഓടിവന്നവനാകട്ടെ,","arabic":"وَأَمَّا مَن جَآءَكَ يَسۡعَىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5766,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-ammā man jāaka yasʿā ","translations":["But as for","(he) who","came to you","striving","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-ammā","man","jāaka","yasʿā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1740],[2,1740,2860],[3,2860,5010],[4,5010,6085]]}},{"name":"80:9","price":"(അല്ലാഹുവെ) അവന്‍ ഭയപ്പെടുന്നവനായിക്കൊണ്ട്‌ (ആകുന്നു വന്നത്).","arabic":"وَهُوَ يَخۡشَىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5767,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"wahuwa yakhshā ","translations":["While he","fears","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["wahuwa","yakhshā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,570],[2,570,1635]]}},{"name":"80:10","price":"അവന്‍റെ കാര്യത്തില്‍ നീ അശ്രദ്ധകാണിക്കുന്നു.(1)","arabic":"فَأَنتَ عَنۡهُ تَلَهَّىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5768,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"1) നബി(ﷺ) ഒരിക്കല്‍ ചില ഖുറൈശി പ്രമുഖന്മാരുമായി സംസാരിച്ചുകൊണ്ടിരിക്കുകയായിരുന്നു. അവര്‍ ഇസ്‌ലാം സ്വീകരിക്കുമെന്ന പ്രതീക്ഷയിലായിരുന്നു അവിടുന്ന് (ﷺ). ആ സന്ദര്‍ഭത്തിലാണ് അന്ധനായ അബ്ദുല്ലാഹി ബ്‌നു ഉമ്മിമക്തൂം റസൂല്‍(ﷺ)നോട് ഇസ്‌ലാമികാദര്‍ശങ്ങള്‍ പഠിപ്പിച്ചുകൊടുക്കാന്‍ ആവശ്യപ്പെട്ടുകൊണ്ട് അങ്ങോട്ട് കടന്നുചെന്നത്. ഒരു പാവപ്പെട്ടവന് നല്കുന്ന പരിഗണന ആ പ്രമുഖന്മാര്‍ക്ക് ഇഷ്ടപ്പെടാതെ വരികയും, അവര്‍ ഇസ്‌ലാമിനോട് തന്നെ വിമുഖത കാണിക്കാന്‍ അത് കാരണമാകുകയും ചെയ്‌തെങ്കിലോ എന്ന ആശങ്ക നിമിത്തം റസൂല്‍ (ﷺ) ആ അന്ധന്റെ ആഗമനത്തില്‍ അസന്തുഷ്ടി പ്രകടിപ്പിച്ചു. അത് ശരിയായില്ലെന്ന് ചൂണ്ടിക്കാണിച്ചുകൊണ്ടാണ് അല്ലാഹു ഈ വചനങ്ങള്‍ അവതരിപ്പിച്ചത്. വിശുദ്ധ ഖുര്‍ആന്‍ നബി(ﷺ)യുടെ സ്വന്തം വചനങ്ങളല്ലെന്നതിനും, വിശുദ്ധ ഖുര്‍ആനില്‍ എന്തെങ്കിലും കൂട്ടുകയോ കുറയ്ക്കുകയോ ചെയ്യാന്‍ നബി(ﷺ)ക്ക് സ്വാതന്ത്ര്യമുണ്ടായിരുന്നില്ലെന്നതിനും പ്രബലമായ ഒരു തെളിവുകൂടിയാണ് ഈ വചനങ്ങള്‍.","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-anta ʿanhu talahhā ","translations":["But you","from him","(are) distracted","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-anta","ʿanhu","talahhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1310],[2,1310,1940],[3,1940,3135]]}},{"name":"80:11","price":"നിസ്സംശയം ഇത് (ഖുര്‍ആന്‍) ഒരു ഉല്‍ബോധനമാകുന്നു; തീര്‍ച്ച.","arabic":"كَلَّآ إِنَّهَا تَذۡكِرَةٞ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5769,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā innahā tadhkiratun ","translations":["Nay","Indeed, it","(is) a reminder","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","innahā","tadhkiratun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2699],[2,2699,4269],[3,4269,5804]]}},{"name":"80:12","price":"അതിനാല്‍ ആര്‍ ഉദ്ദേശിക്കുന്നുവോ അവനത് ഓര്‍മിച്ച് കൊള്ളട്ടെ.","arabic":"فَمَن شَآءَ ذَكَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5770,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"faman shāa dhakarahu ","translations":["So whosoever","wills","may remember it","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["faman","shāa","dhakarahu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,940],[2,940,3370],[3,3370,4535]]}},{"name":"80:13","price":"ആദരണീയമായ ചില ഏടുകളിലാണത്‌.(2)","arabic":"فِي صُحُفٖ مُّكَرَّمَةٖ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5771,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"2) ഉന്നതലോകത്ത് അല്ലാഹുവിന്റെ വചനങ്ങള്‍ ആലേഖനം ചെയ്തിട്ടുള്ള സുഭദ്രമായ രേഖകളെപ്പറ്റിയാണ് ഈ പരാമര്‍ശം എന്നാണ് പ്രമുഖ വ്യാഖ്യാതാക്കളുടെ അഭിപ്രായം.","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"fī ṣuḥufin mukarramatin ","translations":["In","sheets","honored","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["fī","ṣuḥufin","mukarramatin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,430],[2,430,1160],[3,1160,3425]]}},{"name":"80:14","price":"ഔന്നത്യം നല്‍കപ്പെട്ടതും പരിശുദ്ധമാക്കപ്പെട്ടതുമായ (ഏടുകളില്‍).","arabic":"مَّرۡفُوعَةٖ مُّطَهَّرَةِۭ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5772,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"marfūʿatin muṭahharatin ","translations":["Exalted","purified","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["marfūʿatin","muṭahharatin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1410],[2,1410,3795]]}},{"name":"80:15","price":"ചില സന്ദേശവാഹകരുടെ കൈകളിലാണത്‌.","arabic":"بِأَيۡدِي سَفَرَةٖ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5773,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"bi-aydī safaratin ","translations":["In (the) hands","(of) scribes","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["bi-aydī","safaratin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1010],[2,1010,2125]]}},{"name":"80:16","price":"മാന്യന്‍മാരും പുണ്യവാന്‍മാരും ആയിട്ടുള്ളവരുടെ.","arabic":"كِرَامِۭ بَرَرَةٖ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5774,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang"